narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I'd recommend it if you're interested in learning about how soccer interacts with other elements of society and culture.
Fantastic course, I highly recommend it for anyone with a remote interest in soccer looking to improve their writing ability.

I found the class to be interesting because I like sports, so it made reading about different sports while learning to write better. If you are not interested in reading large amounts and always working on a paper, I would suggest finding a different course.
